OL,3,CCompensation for unfairly dismissed
OL,4,Cworkers to increase
OL,6,FJersey's government will raise
OL,7,Fcompensation caps for staff who lose
OL,8,Fout when their employers break the law.
OL,10,FThe Jersey Employment Forum
OL,11,Frecommended the increases after an
OL,12,Fisland-wide consultation earlier this
OL,13,Fyear found that people felt
OL,14,Fcompensation limits were inadequate.
OL,16,FLawyers are now urging businesses to
OL,17,Ffamiliarise themselves with their
OL,18,Flegal obligations to their staff
OL,19,Fbefore the government enact the
OL,20,Fchanges.
