OL,3,CCompensation for unfairly dismissed
OL,4,Cworkers to increase
OL,6,FThe Forum's chair, Carla Benest, said:
OL,7,F"Having greater financial compensation
OL,8,Flimits adds a bit of pressure on those
OL,9,Fbusinesses to ensure that they are
OL,10,Fadopting the correct practices.
OL,12,F"It also enables individuals to bring
OL,13,Ftheir claims and ensure they're going
OL,14,Fto get the recompense they deserve."
OL,16,FAlongside compensation limit
OL,17,Fincreases, the Forum recommends giving
OL,18,Fgreater powers to Jersey's Employment
OL,19,Fand Discrimination Tribunal, which
OL,20,Fdealt with 232 claims last year.
