OL,3,CCompensation for unfairly dismissed
OL,4,Cworkers to increase
OL,6,FThese include the power to anonymise
OL,7,Fjudgements and increase compensation
OL,8,Flimits for unfair dismissal by 25% if
OL,9,Fan employer's conduct has been
OL,10,Fparticularly shocking.
OL,12,FSocial Security Minister Deputy
OL,13,FLyndsay Feltham, who commissioned the
OL,14,Freview, said she will follow all
OL,15,Frecommendations outlined by the Forum
OL,16,Fand has instructed law officers to
OL,17,Flegislate accordingly.
OL,19,FShe has also pledged to make it law
OL,20,Ffor employers to provide employees
OL,21,Fwith written reasons for dismissal.
