OL,3,CCompensation for unfairly dismissed
OL,4,Cworkers to increase
OL,6,FJersey Chamber of Commerce CEO, Murray
OL,7,FNorton, has concerns that these
OL,8,Fchanges would trigger an increase in
OL,9,Fthe number of claims being made and
OL,10,Fput stress on local businesses.
OL,12,FHe explained: "I think what we're
OL,13,Flikely to see is a raising of the
OL,14,Fstakes. The compensation will move up
OL,15,Fand that means we're likely to have
OL,16,Fmore lawyers involved in tribunal
OL,17,Fcases and more costs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
