OL,6,F"There are also concerns about the
OL,7,Fincreasing numbers of businesses
OL,8,Fhaving to buy employment practices
OL,9,Fliability insurance to cover them
OL,10,Fshould a claim come for such a large
OL,11,Famount of money.
OL,13,F"That means there are going to be more
OL,14,Fcosts for both sides; for employers
OL,15,Fand for employees and I think that's
OL,16,Fcausing some concern."
OL,18,FThe government hope to enact the
OL,19,Fchanges by 2025.
